{
  "stem": "1918.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 329.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We spent Passover in our homes with reduced amounts of food, but we were able to bake matzos, or some people were able to bake it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a regular Seder.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By that time, my father had left for America.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He came with the last ship in 1939-- he left in 1939-- in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he arrived in 1940, I believe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the sole purpose of his journey was to save his six children and his wife.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he spent his entire-- all his energies and all his time in Washington, banging on the doors, give me papers for my precious seven, for my six children and my wife!",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Roosevelt in his, as we now know, in his infinite wisdom, did not give him the papers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we perished, most of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But that was the purpose of my father's coming to America.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the reason he could come to America in the first place because he was a businessman who originally came to America to the World's Fair--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to sell Hungarian wine-- create a Hungarian wine pavilion or some such thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he returned in 10 days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In those days, nobody, almost nobody who came to America would return.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They remained here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when he next went to the American Embassy to ask for another visa that he was to go back to America, they gave it to him without any question because they could trust the man.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He returned.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he went to save his family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Roosevelt administration did dirt to him as it did to everybody else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He probably came with some funds and he had family here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had sisters and a brother and probably tried to do some business.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
